strapiSongs.title: The Paranoid Hallucinations of an Evil Spirit (Deep Within the Hidden Swamp)
strapiSongs.lyrics:
You carry on, living fine
Nothing to wonder
Complacent mind
You are so focused
An assembly line
So relieved so happy
Your time to shine

A void is building
Within your being
Your pseudo world
Delusion’s dream
While you are guided
By other’s ways
You’re being supplanted
In cosmic haze
strapiSongs.credits: Music by Victor Fisher of Reenchantment.
strapiSongs.description: A song about what it's like to wake up from this fake world.
